Interface QueryableGridDialect<T extends Serializable>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of native queries supported by this dialect
    All Superinterfaces:
    GridDialect, Serializable, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface QueryableGridDialect<T extends Serializable>
extends GridDialect
